Share this on WhatsAppSeptember is a special day for Seyi Law. National Daily celebrates the proud father on his daughter’s birthday.

As Tiwa turned 4 today, Seyi Law shared adorable photos of himself and his daughter on his Instagram page as he wished her a happy birthday with some sweet words:

”It’s World TIWA’s Day.
Happy Birthday to Daddy’s Princess.
May the world continue to celebrate the goodness of God in your life.
And may your life continue to give the world joy.
It’s an amazing 4.”

